com%2Fnew-york-nurses-strike-labor-union-staffing-shortage-covid-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enurses%20feeling%20overwhelmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20considering%20a%20career%20change.%20Private-equity-owned%20facilities%20looking%20to%20reduce%20costs%20have%20also%20driven%20the%20rise%20of%20these%20apps%2C%20a%20report%20summary%20from%20the%20Roosevelt%20Institute%20released%20last%20month%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20solution%20that%20hospitals%20are%20using%20is%20apps%20that%20allow%20nurses%20to%20pick%20up%20shifts%20%E2%80%94%20similar%20to%20the%20way%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdriving-uber-lyft-part-time-drivers-loneliness-gig-economy-income-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20claim%20gigs%20driving%20people%20to%20the%20airport.%20Apps%20like%20CareRev%2C%20ShiftMed%2C%20and%20Clipboard%20Health%20pitch%20themselves%20to%20medical%20facilities%2C%20including%20those%20with%20staffing%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20that%20emergency%20help%20that%20they%20need%20to%20keep%20their%20hospital%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20nurse%20in%20Southern%20California%20said.%20The%20nurses%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20asked%20that%20their%20full%20names%20not%20be%20published%20for%20fear%20of%20retaliation%20from%20the%20apps%2C%20but%20BI%20has%20verified%20their%20identity%20and%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECareRev%2C%20Clipboard%2C%20Medely%2C%20and%20ShiftMed%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a8793e8-0c0d-4097-a7b7-5be708c51401%5C%22%3ENurses%20often%20find%20themselves%20'thrown%20into'%20gigs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20nurse%20in%20California%20who%20has%20used%20the%20apps%20CareRev%2C%20Clipboard%20Health%2C%20and%20Medely%20said%20that%20many%20hospitals%20in%20her%20area%20that%20offer%20work%20through%20the%20apps%20don't%20appear%20to%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20hire%20as%20many%20full-time%20nurses%20as%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell-known%20hospitals%20like%20the%20Mayo%20Clinic%20are%20probably%20not%20going%20to%20be%20using%20ShiftMed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20nurse%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20tends%20to%20be%20kind%20of%20smaller%20facilities%20and%20less-funded%20facilities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20facilities%20that%20use%20gig%20apps%2C%20nurses%20working%20through%20the%20apps%20can%20outnumber%20employees.%20At%20one%20intensive%20care%20unit%20where%20she%20has%20worked%2C%20the%20nurse%20in%20Southern%20California%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20eight%20of%20us%2C%20and%20seven%20didn't%20actually%20work%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20go%20to%20these%20hospitals%2C%20especially%20some%20of%20them%2C%20you'll%20see%20only%20the%20app%20people%20and%20some%20travel%20nurses%2C%20and%20that's%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20orientation%20those%20hospitals%20provide%20to%20nurses%20who%20work%20there%20through%20the%20apps%20can%20affect%20the%20kind%20of%20care%20patients%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20hospital%20has%20policies%20and%20procedures%20when%20they%20do%20things%20and%20we%20don't%20get%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20nurse%20in%20Southern%20California%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20read%20the%20booklet%20real%20fast%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20always%20know%20we're%20doing%20our%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20instances%20where%20you%20get%20thrown%20into%20something%20and%20you%20do%20the%20best%20that%20you%20can%2C%20and%20care%20can%20unfortunately%20suffer%20because%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20nurse%20on%20three%20apps%20in%20California%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%2C%20a%20nurse%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20said%20that%20most%20hospitals%20she's%20worked%20in%20have%20required%20workers%20hired%20through%20the%20apps%20to%20have%20at%20least%20one%20year%20of%20nursing%20experience.%20However%2C%20she%20said%20stepping%20into%20a%20new%20hospital%20with%20limited%20training%20can%20be%20challenging%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20this%20level%20of%20experience%20might%20be%20insufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20a%20solid%20foundation%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20not%20the%20environment%20to%20build%20your%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20really%20have%20to%20be%20solid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1d44a8e-9898-43e3-961b-51fff6c96b81%5C%22%3EChallenging%20nursing%20gigs%20often%20come%20with%20higher%20pay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20that%20come%20with%20these%20gigs%2C%20Sarah%20said%20the%20pay%20motivates%20many%20nurses%20to%20give%20them%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20wants%20to%20chase%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20hourly%20rates%20for%20these%20gigs%20vary%20by%20hospital%2C%20the%20nursing%20role%2C%20and%20other%20factors%2C%20nurses%20told%20BI%20that%20they%20often%20pay%20roughly%20double%20what%20they%20make%20in%20their%20regular%20nursing%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%20as%20much%20as%20%24115%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20said%20that%20%2475%20an%20hour%20is%20a%20fairly%20standard%20rate%20in%20her%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20which%20would%20earn%20her%20%24900%20over%20a%20twelve-hour%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I'm%20making%20in%20CareRev%20is%20about%20double%20what%20I%20would%20be%20paid%20as%20a%20staff%20nurse%20for%20the%20hospitals%20in%20this%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nurse%20in%20Southern%20California%20said%20that%20she%20considers%20roughly%20%2490%20an%20hour%20to%20be%20a%20typical%20hourly%20rate.%20That's%20compared%20to%20the%20roughly%20%2480%20an%20hour%20she%20estimated%20that%20a%20very%20experienced%20nurse%20would%20make%20at%20a%20large%20hospital%20in%20her%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20seen%20it%20get%20to%20%24114%20on%20a%20holiday%20like%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nurse%20on%20three%20apps%20in%20California%20said%20she%20earns%20between%20%2430%20and%20%2440%20an%20hour%20at%20her%20main%20nursing%20job%20but%20often%20makes%20between%20%2450%20and%20%2470%20an%20hour%20through%20gig%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20just%20picking%20up%20shifts%20on%20your%20own%20through%20these%20apps%2C%20it's%20more%20profitable%20to%20do%20it%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20nurse%20who%20works%20as%20an%20independent%20contractor%20and%20has%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnurses-gig-work-apps-jobs-hospitals-pay-uber-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737283022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678a8506ae09223df2ba70de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnurses-gig-work-apps-jobs-hospitals-pay-uber-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nurses%20are%20turning%20to%20gig%20work%20apps%20to%20boost%20their%20incomes.%20The%20jobs%20can%20be%20very%20stressful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter%2CJacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnurses-gig-work-apps-jobs-hospitals-pay-uber-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BharatPe%20CEO%20says%2090-hour%20week%20difficult%20to%20clock%20in%2C%20work%20quality%20matters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737282837000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2