iness%20Insider%20that%20a%20strong%20labor%20market%20has%20boosted%20consumer%20discretionary%20stocks.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fglp1-weight-loss-drugs-ozempic-walmart-stock-costco-cocacola-pepsico-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcerns%20about%20GLP-1%20weight%20loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20exacerbated%20the%20decline%20in%20consumer%20staples%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20are%20questioning%20the%20long-term%20impact%20of%20revolutionary%20weight%20loss%20drugs%20like%20Ozempic%20on%20food%20and%20beverage%20companies%2C%20which%20dominate%20the%20Consumer%20Staples%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Sundaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20putting%20aside%20what's%20fundamentally%20driving%20the%20widening%20divergence%20in%20performance%20between%20the%20two%20sectors%2C%20this%20is%20typical%20investor%20behavior%20in%20a%20bull%20market%2C%20according%20to%20Sam%20Stovall%2C%20chief%20investment%20strategist%20at%20CFRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntuitively%2C%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20when%20the%20consumer%20discretionary%20sector%20rises%2C%20so%20too%20does%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20since%20the%20consumer%20discretionary%20sector%20has%20a%2093%25%20correlation%20of%20monthly%20returns%20with%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%26quot%3B%20Stovall%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparatively%2C%20the%20consumer%20staples%20sector%20has%20a%2073%25%20correlation%20to%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20according%20to%20Stovall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20type%20of%20behavior%20investors%20want%20to%20see%20during%20bull%20markets%2C%20as%20it%20confirms%20the%20underlying%20trend%20pushing%20stocks%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20looking%20at%20sector%20returns%20during%20market%20advancers%20and%20declines%2C%20consumer%20discretionary%20is%20an%20outperformer%20during%20advances%20and%20consumer%20staples%20is%20an%20u