%20sign%20the%20non-bank%20lending%20industry%20is%20looking%20to%20get%20creative%20with%20how%20it%20lends.%20Robin%20Judson%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20recruiting%20firm%20Robin%20Judson%20Partners%2C%20said%20that%20while%20her%20firm%20is%20seeing%20demand%20%26quot%3Ball%20over%20the%20map%26quot%3B%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20seniority%2C%20there's%20been%20less%20interest%20in%20generalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20demand%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20the%20straight-down-the-fairway%2C%20plain%2C%20vanilla%20lending%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Instead%2C%20firms%20are%20looking%20for%20talent%20where%20they%20see%20returns%3A%20in%20the%20less%20traveled%20areas%20of%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20hiring%20trends%20in%20the%20booming%20industry%20of%20non-bank%20lending%2C%20also%20known%20as%20private%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d840a7da-80dc-41a6-8428-ae3569e2cdf3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoan-to-own%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcredit-crisis-shadow-banking-commercial-real-estate-debt-bofa-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrivate%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20defaults%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20with%20senior%20lenders.%20The%20default%20rate%20for%20senior%20loans%20nearly%20tripled%20between%20mid-2022%20and%20September%202024%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msci.com%2Fwww%2Fquick-take%2Fsignals-of-distress-in-private%2F04962410771%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMSCI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20distress%20can%20also%20provide%20opportunities%20for%20lenders%20who%20have%20the%20right%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERubinetti%20said%20he%20has%20noticed%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20uptick%26quot%3B%20in%20roles%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-us-these-are-companies-making-cuts-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestructuring%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20last%20year%20as%20more%20direct%20lenders%20look%20to%20invest%20in%20opportunities%20where%20they%20might%20become%20owners%20of%20the%20companies%20they%20are%20lending%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELenders%20are%20also%20following%20in%20the%20footsteps%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportfolio-operations-jobs-rising-stars-of-private-equity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate-equity%20cousins%20and%20investing%20in%20portfolio%20operators%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20can%20help%20steer%20businesses%20that%20defaulted%20on%20their%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20also%20seen%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20credit%20firms%20hiring%20private-equity-style%20portfolio%20operations%20professionals%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubinetti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERubinetti%20estimated%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20largest%20credit-only%20players%20now%20have%20someone%20on%20their%20team%20with%20some%20operational%20portfolio%20management%20skills%2C%20but%20said%20it's%20still%20an%20emerging%20trend%20at%20pure-play%2C%20lending-only%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216e117eb-d967-48db-a5c1-8508d5ac45fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20situations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJudson%20is%20seeing%20a%20lot%20of%20demand%20in%20a%20related%20corner%20of%20the%20market%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspecial-situation-investing-tips-self-taught-hedge-funder-steven-kiel-2020-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20situations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Special%20situations%20lenders%20step%20in%20when%20a%20company%20is%20dealing%20with%20some%20sort%20of%2C%20well%2C%20special%20situation%20and%20needs%20a%20lender%20willing%20to%20write%20a%20complicated%2C%20risky%2C%20and%2C%20conversely%2C%20very%20lucrative%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20fund%20may%20have%20loaned%20money%20to%20a%20company%2C%20and%20the%20loan%20is%20now%20not%20performing%2C%20putting%20the%20fund%20in%20trouble%2C%20too.%20The%20fund%20may%20reach%20out%20to%20another%20fund%2C%20which%20will%20take%20on%20some%20of%20the%20risk%20of%20that%20loan%20but%20also%20gain%20more%20control%20over%20the%20business%20in%20the%20meantime.%20Writing%20that%20loan%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20risk%2C%20but%20also%20stands%20to%20generate%20very%20high%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20a%20very%20acute%20sense%20of%20risk%20and%20reward%2C%26quot%3B%20Judson%20said%20about%20special-situations%20loan%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20requires%20somebody%20who%20understands%20credit%20and%20leverage%2C%20and%20understands%20how%20to%20put%20together%20a%20transaction%20that%20is%20going%20to%20benefit%20everyone%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20Judson%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20provide%20the%20financing%20a%20company%20needs%20and%20a%20return%20that%20a%20fund%20is%20looking%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudson%20is%20seeing%20demand%20for%20special-situation%20credit%20experts%20from%20independent%20private%20credit%20funds%20and%20megafunds%20as%20well%20as%20private-equity%20firms%20with%20industry-specific%2C%20multi-asset%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20job%20listings%2C%20lender%20and%20asset%20manager%20Golub%20Capital%20is%20hiring%20an%20associate%20for%20its%20direct%20lending%20workout%20group%20and%20special-situations%20team.%20The%20associate%20would%20help%20the%20firm%20with%20%26quot%3Bmaximizing%20recoveries%20and%20minimizing%20losses%26quot%3B%20and%20may%20require%20%26quot%3Boperational%20turnarounds.%26quot%3B%20The%20base%20salary%20for%20New%20York-based%20hires%20is%20%24170%2C000%20to%20%24185%2C000%20and%20likely%20includes%20a%20bonus%20as%20well%2C%20the%20listing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d179089b-2077-4f6f-b482-1cd6abe58f09%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsset-backed%20finance%20and%20other%20specialties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProfessionals%20who%20specialize%20in%20complicated%20and%20lucrative%20types%20of%20loans%20or%20lending%20to%20in-demand%20industries%20are%20also%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20in%20today's%20job%20market%2C%20recruiters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20we%20see%20is%20in%20the%20corners%20of%20the%20market%20where%20the%20structures%20and%20the%20issues%20are%20more%20complex%20and%20juicy%2C%26quot%3B%20Judson%20said.%20In%20these%20niches%2C%20lenders%20can%20differentiate%20themselves%20from%20the%20competition%20through%20how%20they%20structure%20and%20manage%20their%20loans%2C%20and%20drive%20higher%20returns%20as%20well%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERubinetti%20said%20that%20he's%20seen%20the%20most%20interest%20recently%20in%20niches%20such%20as%20alternative%20credit%2C%20asset-based%20lending%2C%20and%20specialty%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20firms%20don't%20have%20this%20capability%20now%2C%20they%20want%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubinetti%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20small%20area%2C%20but%20far%20and%20away%2C%20it's%20been%20the%20most%20active%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-market-asset-management-deal-outlook-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECorporate%20consolidation%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20just%20how%20much%20interest%20there%20is%20in%20some%20niche%20lending%20strategies.%20Janus%20Henderson%20acquired%20asset-backed%20lender%20Victory%20Park%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%20to%20provide%20its%20clients%20a%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20in-demand%20asset-backed-focused%20private%20credit%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Ali%20Dibadj%2C%20CEO%20of%20Janus%20Henderson%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERubinetti%20has%20seen%20job%20demand%20for%20lending%20roles%20in%20equipment%20leasing%2C%20aviation%20finance%2C%20consumer%20finance%2C%20or%20any%20industry%20with%20real%2