Bbarely%20enough%20to%20cover%20basic%20living%20expenses%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20stressful.%20She%20started%20to%20think%20about%20other%20ways%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zara%20Dar%20and%20her%20YouTube%20play%20button%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F677fcbd2f83fcec7e5b52e55%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZara%20Dar%20and%20her%20plaque%20from%20YouTube%2C%20marking%20her%20achieving%20100%2C000%20subscribers.%3Cp%3EZara%20Dar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22930358ce-1c7e-40eb-8118-7aab11a39fba%5C%22%3EHer%20STEM%20niche%20led%20to%20OnlyFans%20promoting%20her%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDar%20found%20that%20her%20STEM%20niche%20set%20her%20apart%20on%20OnlyFans%2C%20which%20promoted%20her%20videos%20on%20its%20main%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20YouTube%20channel%20recently%20reached%20150%2C000%20subscribers.%20Her%20videos%20include%20explanations%20of%20neural%20networks%2C%20machine%20learning%20concepts%2C%20and%20how%20she%20developed%20her%20own%20OnlyFans%20notification%20robot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20made%20me%20realize%20I%20can%20have%20an%20actual%20career%20by%20continuing%20to%20share%20educational%20and%20artistic%20content%20on%20OnlyFans%2C%26quot%3B%20Dar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDar%20has%20had%20setbacks.%20Her%20Instagram%2C%20where%20she%20discussed%20topics%20such%20as%20the%20Leidenfrost%20effect%20and%20Schr%C3%B6dinger's%20cat%2C%20was%20banned%20for%20sexual%20content%20because%20she%20was%20showing%20cleavage%2C%20which%20put%20a%20dent%20in%20her%20earnings.%20The%20account%20has%20since%20been%20reinstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20focused%20more%20on%20her%20social%20media%20presence%20since%20quitting%20her%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20YouTube%20video%20about%20dropping%20out%20of%20her%20doctorate%20made%20Zar%20%2440%2C000%20in%20