0Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20while%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20has%20recently%20retired%20from%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSurya%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20squad%2C%20he%20is%20a%20360%20player%20who%20can%20score%20at%209%20runs%20per%20over%20at%20any%20stage%20of%20the%20game.%20He%20can%20dominate%20the%20opposition%20and%20bats%20in%20a%20different%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Raina%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports%20Press%20Room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Surya%20was%20there%20there%20would%20have%20been%20an%20X-factor%2C%20he%20will%20be%20missed.%20The%20responsibility%20will%20be%20now%20on%20top%203%20who%20are%20not%20in%20form.%20Surya%20is%20someone%20who%20can%20bat%20in%20any%20position.%26quot%3B%20Raina%20also%20said%20with%20uncertainty%20looming%20large%20over%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20fitness%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami%20returning%20from%20an%20injury%2C%20Siraj%20would%20have%20been%20a%20better%20option%20although%20he%20still%20feels%2C%20the%20Hyderabad%20pacer%20can%20still%20make%20it%20to%20the%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSiraj%20was%20in%20a%20different%20form%20in%20Australia%20but%20you%20can%20change%20the%20squad%20till%2012%20February.%20So%20I%20feel%20Siraj%20can%20be%20back%20in%20the%20side%20if%20Bumrah%20is%20not%20fully%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarshit%20Rana%20has%20done%20well.%20He%20has%20good%20pace%2C%20good%20bumper%2C%20variation%2C%20yorker%20and%20pace.%20He%20and%20both%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20can%20bowl%20at%20the%20death%20but%20I%20still%20feel%2C%20Siraj%20is%20a%20better%20option%20if%20Bumrah%20is%20not%20there.%26quot%3B%20While%20Bumrah%20is%20racing%20against%20time%20to%20be%20fit%20from%20back%20spasms%20that%20he%20suffered%20during%20the%20recent%20Sydney%20Test%20against%20Australia%2C%20Shami%20is%20returning%20to%20the%20ODI%20set%20up%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20after%20recovering%20from%20a%2