ions-trophy-squad-feels-suresh-raina%2Farticleshow%2F117369947.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20cricketer%20Suresh%20Raina%20believes%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20team%20can%20replicate%20MS%20Dhoni's%202013%20Champions%20Trophy%20victory.%20However%2C%20he%20criticizes%20the%20exclusion%20of%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20pointing%20out%20his%20significant%20impact%20and%20flexibility%20in%20the%20middle%20order.%20The%20tournament%20begins%20on%20February%2019%2C%202025%2C%20with%20India's%20first%20match%20against%20Bangladesh.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20India%20men's%20cricket%20team%20Chairman%20of%20selectors%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20and%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20unveiled%20the%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20set%20to%20begin%20on%20February%2019%20in%20Karachi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AMIT%20KUMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findia-missing-x-factor-suryakumar-yadav-in-champions-trophy-squad-feels-suresh-raina%2Farticleshow%2F117369947.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rohit%20Is%20Weak%2C%20Virat%20Only...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-India%20Star%20Drops%20%26quot%3BMentally%20Fit%26quot%3B%20Bombshell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20cricketer%20Surinder%20Khanna%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20omission%20of%20Karun%20Nair%20from%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20squad%20despite%20an%20exceptional%20performer%20in%20first-class%20cricket.%20Ajit%20Agarkar%20and%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20held%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Saturday%20to%20announce%20the%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20and%20ODI%20series%20against%20England.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Karun%20Nair%20is%20a%20bit%20unlucky.%20I%20wish%20I%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20selectors.%20He%20hit%20300%20in%20the%20test%20match%2C%20and%20after%20that%20he%20disappeared.%20Now%20suddenly%20the%20moon%20has%20come%20out%20again%2C%20so%20that%20moon%20should%20shine%20for%202-3%20years%20and%20how%20many%2035-36%20year%20olds%20can%20you%20have%20in%20the%20team%3F%20It's%20a%20one-day%20format%2C%20you%20require%20quick%20movers%20in%20the%20fielding%2C%26quot%3B%20Surinder%20Khanna%20said%20while%20speaking%20to%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENair%20was%20the%20top-run-getter%20not%20only%20for%20Vidarbha%20but%20also%20in%20the%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%202024-25%2C%20having%20accumulated%20a%20massive%20779%20runs%20in%20seven%20matches%20at%20a%20mind-boggling%20average%20of%20389.50%20as%20he%20has%20remained%20unbeaten%20in%20six%20innings.%20Even%20after%20his%20stupendous%20performance%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20failed%20to%20find%20a%20spot%20in%20the%2015-member%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20six%20Tests%20for%20India%20since%20his%20debut%20in%202016%2C%20he%20made%20374%20runs%20in%20seven%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2062.33%2C%20with%20best%20score%20of%20303*.%20Nair%20also%20played%20two%20ODIs%20for%20India%2C%20scoring%2046%20runs%20with%20best%20score%20of%2039.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%2068-year-old%20raised%20questions%20on%20Rohit%20and%20stalwart%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli's%20fitness%20and%20said%20that%20they%20both%20should%20get%20%26quot%3Bmentally%20fit%26quot%3B%20and%20focus%20on%20their%20games%20to%20come%20back%20to%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20captain%20is%20also%20weak.%20I%20mean%2C%20if%20you%20make%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20field%20on%20the%20boundary%2C%20then%20two%20runs%20will%20be%20easily%20taken.%20Virat%20Kohli%20also%20fields%20in%20slips%20and%20only%20does%20fielding%20inside%20the%20circle.%20Kohli%20is%20not%20making%20runs%20in%20the%20fielding%2C%20he%20is%20putting%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20effort%20in%20the%20circle.%20I%20hope%20they%20all%20get%20fit%20mentally%20and%20focus%20and%20come%20back%20to%20their%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Surinder%20Khanna%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20came%20under%20fire%20for%20an%20underwhelming%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20campaign%20and%20overall%20a%20very%20disappointing%202024%2F25%20season%20of%20Test%20cricket.%20Sharma%20(31%20runs%20in%20three%20matches%20and%20five%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%206.20)%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20(190%20runs%20in%20five%20matches%20and%20nine%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2023.75%20with%20a%20century)%20lacked%20big%20time%20with%20the%20bat.%20Virat%20fell%20for%20the%20outside-off-stump%20trap%20throughout%20the%20series%2C%20most%20notably%20by%20pacer%20Scott%20Boland%20who%20dismissed%20him%20four%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202024-25%20season%20of%20Tests%20has%20been%20miserable%20for%20'Ro-Ko'%20(Rohit%20and%20Kohli).%20While%20Rohit%20scored%20just%20164%20runs%20in%20eight%20matches%20and%2015%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2010.93%20with%20best%20score%20of%2052%2C%20Virat%20scored%20a%20shambolic%20382%20runs%20in%2010%20matches%20and%2019%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2022.87%2C%20with%20just%20a%20century%20and%20fifty%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20the%20former%20cricketer%20lauded%20the%20management's%20decision%20to%20elect%20Shubman%20Gill%20as%20the%20vice-captain%20of%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20good%20and%20positive%20development.%20The%20new%20generation%20who%20want%20to%20take%20captainship%20from%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20have%20been%20given%20leadership%20roles.%20When%20Shubman%20Gill%20was%20sent%20to%20Zimbabwe%20as%20a%20captain%2C%20he%20went%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20places.%20The%20youngster%20has%20shown%20promise.%20Gill%20has%20to%20get%20his%20form%2C%20that's%20the%20main%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Surinder%20Khanna%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20freshest%20challenge%20awaiting%20India%20is%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20starting%20from%20February%2019%20till%20March%209.%20It%20will%20be%20hosted%20by%20Pakistan%20and%20UAE%2C%20with%20India%20playing%20its%20matches%20in%20UAE%20under%20a%20hybrid%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight-team%20tournament%20will%20feature%2015%2050-over%20matches%20and%20will%20be%20played%20across%20Pakistan%20and%20in%20Dubai.%20The%20biggest%20match%20of%20the%20tournament%20between%20two%20arch-rivals%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20be%20played%20on%20February%2023.%20India%20will%20start%20its%20campaign%20against%20Bangladesh%20on%20February%2020.%20India's%20last%20league%20match%20will%20be%20against%20New%20Zealand%20on%20March%202.%20The%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20will%20play%20all%20their%20matches%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20squad%20for%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(C)%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20(VC)%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20KL%20Rahul%20(WK)%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Axar%20Patel%2C%20Washington%20Sundar%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737274920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8bnni5p_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-x_625x300_30_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Frohit-sharma-is-weak-virat-kohli-only-ex-india-star-drops-mentally-fit-bombshell-7508101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20cricketer%20Surinder%20Khanna%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20on%20the%20omission%20of%20Karun%20Nair%20from%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20squad%20despite%20an%20exceptional%20performer%20in%20first-class%20cricket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Frohit-sharma-is-weak-virat-kohli-only-ex-india-star-drop