20In%20Thane.%20How%20Cops%20Found%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShariful%20Islam%20Shehzad%2C%20a%20Bangladeshi%20national%20who%20had%20illegally%20entered%20India%20and%20had%20been%20living%20under%20the%20false%20name%20Bijoy%20Das%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20breaking%20into%20actor%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20home%20and%20attacking%20him%20and%20his%20staff%20during%20a%20burglary%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20had%20formed%2030%20teams%20to%20track%20down%20the%20accused%2C%20who%20scanned%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20building%20in%20Bandra%20where%20the%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20actor%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%20and%20their%20sons%20live.%20They%20noticed%20the%20suspect%20leaving%20the%20building%20after%20the%20attack%20that%20left%20the%20actor%20seriously%20injured.%20Police%20then%20scanned%20several%20hours%20of%20footage%20from%20across%20the%20city%20to%20locate%20the%20suspect.%20During%20this%20tenous%20exercise%2C%20they%20found%20a%20footage%20captured%20by%20a%20CCTV%20camera%20in%20DN%20Nagar%20in%20Andheri.%20They%20saw%20the%20suspect%20getting%20off%20the%20bike%20and%20tracked%20down%20the%20two-wheeler%20using%20its%20number.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fgeulh2m8_saif-attacker_625x300_19_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParallelly%2C%20following%20local%20intelligence%20inputs%2C%20police%20zeroed%20in%20on%20a%20rented%20accommodation%20at%20Koliwada%20in%20Worli%2C%20where%20the%20accused%20lived%20with%20three%20others%2C%20sources%20in%20police%20said.%20A%20police%20team%20went%20to%20this%20accommodation%20and%20questioned%20the%20people%20living%20there.%20They%20managed%20to%20ge