for-ignoring-him-1600-calls-in-11-months-led-to-arrest%2Farticleshow%2F117369491.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Geeta%20and%20her%20daughter%20Deepika%20were%20murdered%20by%20Geeta's%20paramour%20Vikas%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime%20after%20being%20arrested.%20Jaiswal%2C%20enraged%20by%20Geeta's%20recent%20neglect%2C%20entered%20her%20home%2C%20attacked%20them%2C%20and%20staged%20the%20scene%20as%20a%20robbery.%20Call%20records%20and%20evidence%20led%20to%20his%20arrest%20and%20confession.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PATHIKRIT%20CHAKRABORTY%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Flucknow%2Fobsession-turns-fatal-up-man-murders-woman-child-for-ignoring-him-1600-calls-in-11-months-led-to-arrest%2Farticleshow%2F117369491.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump's%20Inauguration%20Celebrations%20Kick%20Off%3A%20Venue%2C%20Guest%20List%20And%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20set%20to%20take%20charge%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20reached%20Washington%20on%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20ahead%20of%20his%20inauguration%20ceremony%20marking%20his%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%20The%20incoming%20President's%20inaugural%20weekend%20began%20with%20a%20star-studded%20500-member%20reception%20at%20the%20Trump%20National%20Golf%20Club%20in%20Virginia%2C%20which%20included%20his%20cabinet%20nominees%20Pete%20Hegseth%20and%20Lee%20Zeldin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incoming%20commander-in-chief%20posted%20a%20nearly%2015-minute%20video%20from%20the%20event%20showcasing%20him%20and%20First%20Lady%20Melania%20standing%20beside%20each%20other%20on%20a%20balcony%20at%20his%20golf%20club%20and%20applauding%20the%20massive%20pyrotechnic%20display.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20video%2C%20the%20soon-to-be%20President%20can%20be%20seen%20shaking%20his%20leg%20and%20performing%20one%20of%20his%20signature%20dance%20moves%20in%20front%20of%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20Inauguration%20Gala%20Details%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrations%20Start%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E-Mr%20Trump's%20inaugural%20ceremony%20includes%2018%20galas%2C%20with%20three%20official%20events%20that%20the%20Present-elect%20is%20expected%20to%20attend.%20The%20celebrations%20kicked%20off%20with%20a%20gala%20at%20Trump%20National%20Golf%20Club%20in%20Virginia%20on%20Sunday.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20President-elect%20arrived%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20where%20he's%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20rally%20and%20a%20candlelit%20dinner%20with%20supporters%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20alone%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20a%20major%20%26quot%3BMake%20America%20Great%20Again%20Victory%20Rally%26quot%3B%20at%20Capital%20One%20Arena%20for%20his%20supporters.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20first%20such%20event%20in%20the%20US%20capital%20that%20Mr%20Trump%20will%20address%20since%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20Ellipse%20on%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20Capital%20riots.%20Later%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20he%20is%20also%20scheduled%20to%20attend%20a%20candlelight%20dinner%20with%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Inauguration%20Ceremony-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0Mr%20Trump%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%2047th%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20at%2012%20pm%20EST%20(10%3A30%20pm%20IST)%20on%20Monday%20as%20the%20US%20Constitution%20mandates%20that%20each%20new%20president's%20term%20begins%20at%20noon%20on%20January%2020%20(or%20the%20day%20after%20if%20it%20falls%20on%20a%20Sunday).%20The%20oath%20is%20most%20often%20administered%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20chief%20justice%2C%20and%20Monday%20would%20mark%20John%20Roberts's%20second%20time%20officiating%20for%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20First%20Address-%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20new%20president%20is%20then%20expected%20to%20deliver%20an%20inaugural%20address%2C%20laying%20out%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years.%20The%20Republican%20rang%20in%20his%20first%20term%20in%202017%20by%20evoking%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20carnage.%26quot%3B%20Incoming%20vice%20president%20JD%20Vance%20will%20also%20be%20sworn%20in%20during%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInaugural%20Luncheon-%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EFollowing%20the%20ceremony%2C%20the%20President%2C%20along%20with%20their%20spouse%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Senate%20leaders%2C%20and%20distinguished%20guests%2C%20would%20be%20escorted%20to%20Statuary%20Hall%20in%20the%20US%20Capitol%20for%20a%20celebratory%20luncheon%20hosted%20by%20the%20Joint%20Congressional%20Committee%20on%20Inaugural%20Ceremonies%20(JCCIC).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOval%20Office%20Signings-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20first%20act%20as%20the%20President%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20likely%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20traditional%20signing%20of%20executive%20orders%2C%20officially%20beginning%20his%20second%20administration.%20The%20incoming%20President%20has%20pledged%20to%20fulfil%20a%20number%20of%20his%20poll%20promises%20on%20Day%201%20by%20signing%20executive%20orders%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20issues%20will%20be%20first%20up.%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20likely%20to%20reinstate%20some%20executive%20orders%20from%20his%20first%20term%20that%20President%20Biden%20had%20revoked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInaugural%20Balls-%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20signing%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20three%20official%20inaugural%20balls%20on%20Monday%20evening.%20Mr%20Trump%20is%20expected%20to%20attend%20all%20three%20galas%20--%20the%20Commander%20in%20Chief%20Ball%2C%20the%20Liberty%20Ball%20and%20the%20Starlight%20Ball.%20More%20than%20a%20dozen%20other%20events%20are%20also%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENational%20Prayer%20Service-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mr%20Trump%20will%20be%20hosted%20by%20the%20Washington%20National%20Cathedral%2C%20the%20sexy%20day%20after%20his%20inauguration%20at%2011%20am%20(9%3A30%20pm%20IST)%20on%20Tuesday%20for%20an%20interfaith%20prayer%20service.%20The%20service%20will%20mark%20the%20official%20conclusion%20of%20the%20inauguration%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EChange%20In%20Swearing-In%20Venue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20presidents%20traditionally%20assume%20their%20powers%20outdoors%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Capitol%20building%2C%20with%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20spectators%20witnessing%20the%20ceremony%2C%20Mr%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20said%20he%20would%20move%20the%20event%20inside%20the%20Capitol%20Rotunda%20amid%20forecasts%20of%20extreme%20cold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrowd%20size%20is%20a%20preoccupation%20of%20%C2%A0Mr%20Trump's%2C%20but%20the%20last-minute%20switch%20to%20an%20indoor%20event%20may%20dent%20his%20bragging%20rights.%20More%20than%20220%2C000%20tickets%20were%20being%20distributed%20to%20the%20public%20before%20the%20incoming%20President's%20announcement%20of%20shifting%20the%20venue%20to%20the%20Capitol%20Rotunda%2C%20which%20can%20accommodate%20only%20about%20600%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20supporters%20could%20watch%20a%20live%20feed%20from%20Washington's%20Capital%20One%20sports%20arena%2C%20which%20holds%20up%20to%2020%2C000%20--%20and%20he%20promised%20to%20drop%20in%20later.%20%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20a%20very%20beautiful%20experience%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president-elect%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresidential%20Parade%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president's%20inaugural%20parade%20will%20be%20held%20inside%20for%20the%20first%20since%201985.%20The%20parade%2C%20which%20has%20followed%20the%20presidential%20entourage%20down%20Pennsylvania%20Avenue%20as%20far%20back%20as%201805%2C%20will%20march%20on%20inside%20Capital%20One%20Arena%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20after%20Mr%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20announced%20that%20he%20would%20take%20oath%20and%20deliver%20his%20inaugural%20address%20inside%20the%20US%20Capitol%20Rotunda%20and%20promoted%20Capital%20One%20Arena%20as%20essentially%20a%20massive%20watch%20party%20venue%20for%20his%20oath%20of%20office%20and%20inaugural%20address%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusical%20Affair%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump's%20inauguration%202.0%20will%20be%20a%20star-studded%20affair%2C%20with%20country%20star%20Carrie%20Underwood%20singing%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20the%20Beautiful%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20performing%20will%20be%20country%20singer%20Lee%20Greenwood%2C%20whose%20patriotic%20anthem%20%26quot%3BGod%20Bless%20the%20USA%26quot%3B%20is%20standard%20at%20Trump%20rallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pre-inauguration%20rally%20on%20Sunday%20will%20include%20a%20performance%20by%20the%20Village%20People%2C%20whose%201970s-era%20%26quot%3BY.M.C.A.%26quot%3B%20is%20another%20Trump%20event%20staple%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20Kid%20Rock%20and%20Billy%20Ray%20Cyrus.%20Country%20musicians%20including%20Jason%20Aldean%2C%20Rascal%20Flatts%20and%20Gavin%20DeGraw%20plus%20the%20Village%20People%20will%20perform%20across%20Trump's%20three%20official%20inaugural%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInaugural%20Lunch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20became%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20day's%20events%20in%201897%2C%20when%20the%20Senate%20Committee%20on%20Arrangements%20arranged%20a%20meal%20for%20President%20William%20McKinley%2C%20symbolizing%20the%20transition%20of%20power%20and%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20menu%20for%20Donald%20Trump's%202025%20Inaugural%20Luncheon%20has%20not%20been%20revealed%20yet%2C%20but%20it%20is%20likely%20to%20follow%20patterns%20of%20previous%20occasions%20and%20may%20include%20the%20great%20American%20classic%20cuisines.%20As%20Mr%20Trump%20reportedly%20enjoys%20simple%2C%20savoury%20meals%2C%20he%20might%20include%20steak%20with%20some%20lobster%2C%20together%20with%20exquisite%20sweets.%20The%20Gulf%20shrimp%20and%20regional%20American%20flavours%20were%20part%20of%20his%20inauguration%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuest%20List%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republican%20has%20invited%20a%20number%20of%20tech%20titans%20to%20attend%20the%20inauguration%2C%20joining%20more%20traditional%20guests%20such%20as%20his%20cabinet%20nominees.%20Billionaires%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20will%20attend%20as%20will%20Shou%20Chew%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Chinese%20social%20media%20giant%20TikTok%2C%20according%20to%20US%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20has%20courted%20closer%20ties%20with%20the%20tech%20moguls%2C%20and%20his%20campaign%20benefited%20from%20disinformation%20spread%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20such%20as%20TikTok%2C%20Musk's%20X%20and%20Zuckerberg's%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20will%20also%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20--%20despite%20Trump's%20refusal%20to%20appear%20at%20Biden's%20swearing-in%20when%20he%20beat%20Trump%20in%202020.%20All%20living%20former%20presidents%20--%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20George%20W.%20Bush%20and%20Barack%20Obama%20--%20will%20attend%2C%20as%20will%20their%20wives%2C%20except%20for%20Michelle%20Obama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20whom%20Trump%20beat%20in%20the%202016%20presidential%20election%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20whom%20he%20beat%20in%20November%2C%20will%20be%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeads%20of%20state%20are%20not%20traditionally%20invited%2C%20but%20Trump%20has%20sent%20invitations%20to%20a%20handful%20of%20foreign%20leaders%2C%20including%20some%20who%20share%20his%20right-wing%20politics.%20Fa