%20on%20camera%20brutally%20assaulting%20a%20man%20standing%20near%20the%20Governor's%20convoy.%20The%20video%2C%20now%20viral%2C%20shows%20the%20traffic%20constable%20shoving%20the%20man%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20kicking%20him%2C%20and%20then%20slapping%20him%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20get%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20at%20Anand%20Nagar%20intersection%2C%20where%20the%20Governor's%20convoy%20was%20passing%20through.%20The%20man%2C%20who%20appeared%20to%20be%20standing%20near%20the%20convoy%2C%20drew%20the%20immediate%20ire%20of%20the%20traffic%20police.%20Without%20any%20apparent%20provocation%2C%20a%20constable%20rushed%20towards%20him%2C%20assaulting%20him%20in%20full%20public%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20sparked%20outrage%20on%20social%20media%2C%20prompting%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%20for%20Traffic%20to%20order%20a%20thorough%20investigation.%20Additional%20DCP%20Vikram%20Raghuvanshi%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20Governor%20is%20under%20Z%2B%20security%2C%20and%20no%20one%20is%20allowed%20near%20the%20convoy%20due%20to%20the%20potential%20risk%20of%20accidents.%20The%20ACP%20Traffic%20Police%20is%20now%20tasked%20with%20examining%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20identifying%20the%20victim%20and%20circumstances%20leading%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20convoy%20of%20His%20Excellency%20the%20Governor%2C%20who%20has%20Z%2B%20security.%20The%20motorcade%20moves%20at%20high%20speed%2C%20and%20despite%20being%20warned%20by%20the%20police%2C%20the%20individual%20still%20approached%20the%20convoy.%20You%20are%20unidentified-why%20are%20you%20going%20near%20the%20convoy%3F%20An%20investigation%20has%20been%20ordered%20into%20this%20matter.%20The%20DCP%20has%20directed%20an%20ACP-level%20officer%20to%20conduct%20the%20inquiry.%20They%20have%20retrieved%20video%20footage%20and%20started%20recording%20statements.%20Investigations%20take%20time%2C%20but%20the%20facts%20will%20e