20father%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20merchant%20navy%20at%20the%20time%2C%20quit%20and%20took%20over%20the%20business.%20In%20the%2070s%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263689%2Findia-nilons-pickles-iconic-brands-suresh-prafful-sanghavi-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epickle%20bottles%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20wrapped%20in%20straw%20and%20put%20into%20wooden%20boxes%20and%20exported.%20But%20the%20journey%20through%20the%20sea%20would%20cause%20the%20bottles%20to%20break.%20My%20father%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20start%20using%20cardboard%20boxes%20for%20packaging.%20This%20sorted%20the%20issue%20of%20breakage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20processes%20at%20the%20new%20factory%20are%20automated%2C%20ensuring%20precision%20and%20consistency%20in%20the%20preserve%20making%20process%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-el