ss%20their%20grief%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20observes.%20%E2%80%9CYet%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20we%20were%20subjected%20to%20such%20widespread%20discrimination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-2%20wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20620px)%20100vw%2C%20620px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20people%20playing%20parai.%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22391636%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739.jpg%20620w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Ffile-12_11zon-1734932739-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391636%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParai%20was%20considered%20as%20an%20instrument%20to%20be%20played%20by%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20lower%20caste%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nigar%20Kalai%20Koodam%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20association%20of%20the%20parai%20with%20alcohol%20significantly%20contributes%20to%20the%20social%20stigma%20surrounding%20its%20players.%20Playing%20the%20instrument%20requires%20immense%20energy%20and%20stamina%2C%20leading%20many%20players%20to%20submit%20to%20alcohol.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20alcohol%20was%20even%20used%20as%20a%20form%20of%20payment%20for%20parai%20players%2C%20further%20reinforcing%20this%20association.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20wear%20slippers